data.description: If you are looking for a large square footage home set up for extended family - look no more!  This spacious 2-story homes interior has been slightly modified to create 2 separate living areas, perfect for an In-Law, adult children at home or simply house sharing. The downstairs primary suite/living area is now a complete apartment with kitchenette. The spacious upstairs has a second primary suite and three more bedrooms.  House boasts a large family kitchen with island, a flex room which can serve as a dining room or office.  Also check out the convenient addition of a full shower and additional washer connection in garage for those sandy beach visits. Don't miss this one!  Note: Please see documents for the floor plan! This property may be eligible for a USDA loan to a qualified buyer. 2023-10-24
